description:
This exceptional four bedroom contemporary residence is peacefully set in a quiet street opposite bushland within the highly sought-after Morisset Meadows Estate, Morisset and nestled amongst quality homes in a tranquil setting. Moments from Sporting Oval, Primary/High Schools, Morisset CBD, Train Station, cafes/restaurants, 2 major Shopping Centres, Waratah Medical Centre and close proximity to the freeway to Sydney and Newcastle. This standout property will definitely impress families, couples, retiree's, entertainers and investors alike for the super convenient location!

• Single level layout and design
• Four bedrooms, 3 featuring built-in wardrobes
• Master suite with walk-in-robe & ensuite
• Spacious open plan kitchen, dining, family & media room
• Great kitchen with breakfast bar, stainless steel oven, gas cooktop & dishwasher
• Modern family bathroom with bathtub & large shower
• Good sized laundry
• Outdoor flow to alfresco area for relaxing
• 40 panel 13.2kw - 2x 5kw twin inverter solar system
• Security camera, gas H.W.S. rainwater tank
• Split system A/C, verticals, drapes, ceiling fans, carpets & LED lights
• Remote double garage with internal access
• Set across approx. 607sqm block with side access
• Concrete driveway leads to 6m x 3.3m shed in backyard.
• Large lush fully fenced backyard, perfect place for children & pets to play safely
• This property will top your list to inspect!
